    <item>
      <title>美联储接近降息，科技股普遍上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/broader-tech-rally-hangs-on-fed-getting-closer-to-cutting-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市的全面上涨并未蔓延至科技板块，该板块的涨幅仍然集中在少数几只人工智能赢家身上，这些股票在宏观经济不确定的背景下已成为防御性股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/broader-tech-rally-hangs-on-fed-getting-closer-to-cutting-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 10:32:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
